snippet.title: Yerr Out gameplay - AVAILABLE NOW on Steam Early Access
snippet.description:
Yerr Out - a wacky & competitive baseball game now available for Steam Early Access!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1963360/Yerr_Out/

Features that will be coming out during the early access period leading up to a full version include:
- 3+ fields to play at
- 42+ characters (currently 30)
- online PvP + leaderboards
